public interface AsyncObject3DListener

Summary

Public methods

abstract void onObject3DFailed(String error)

Invoked on the main thread if an Object3D fails to load.

abstract void onObject3DLoaded(Object3D object, Object3D.Type type)

Invoked on main thread after the Object3D is loaded.
